[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-04-05-aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"世紀帝國 II 系列：將中文介面下預設房間名稱改回英文","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我寫了第二個模組並發佈到 Steam 工作坊了！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1352725205","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Steam 工作坊 :: English Room Name in Chinese UI"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我想多數台灣玩家在玩 AoE II:HD 時，都會訂閱由 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steamcommunity.com/id/ZoeyHsieh","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zoey Meow"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 製作的繁體中文化模組 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=466768643","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TChinese Zoey’s Work"}]},{"type":"text","value":"吧（嗯？這句好眼熟）。然而目前 AoE2:HD 尚未完整支援中文，尤其是在多人連線進度的儲存上，仍會時常遇到問題：倘若房間名稱包含中文時，會導致無法儲存遊戲，並且跳出類似於下面的訊息："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫入多人連線存擋遊戲時發生錯誤！你的磁碟空間可能已經用完。無法打開文件: C\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Age2HD\\savegame\\multi\\Ruoshi的房間-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx.aoe2mpgame"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"或是如下圖："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"![AoE2HD-English-Room-Name-mod 1.png](AoE2HD-English-Room-Name-mod 1.png)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以每次和朋友打團時，總要不免其煩的更改房間名稱，改久了也是會發懶的。於是朋友就提到，我既然已經會建立模組了，何不順便寫一個模組，讓房間名稱是英文的呢？這一聽之下覺得可行，就動手做了，馬上將願望成真！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"畢竟這是遊戲本身的問題，你要中文化模組作者再把房間名稱從「<玩家>的房間」改回「<玩家>’s game」也說不過去。這時候若有一個小模組能讓我們享受中文化模組的同時，也能不用再改房間名稱，等日後官方解決這個缺陷，再將這個小模組停用，這豈不是皆大歡喜。XD"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"於是本模組就誕生啦！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前 AoE2:HD 尚未完整支援中文，尤其是在多人連線進度的儲存上，仍會時常遇到問題，導致遇到狀況無法先儲存再另外打過。但是每次開房都要更改房間名稱，又實在是一件很繁瑣且容易忘記的事情。本模組則是幫助使用中文語系的玩家們，在開房時房名仍維持英文語系的預設值，不再需要另外改名稱、或是因為忘記改名稱而懊悔啦！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"簡單來說，就是讓本模組將被中文化模組翻譯過的房名從「<玩家>的房間」再改回英文版預設的「<玩家>’s game」，讓我們不用在因為忘記改房名導致無法存檔囉！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若好奇這個模組是怎麼運作的，本模組的相關程式碼與資源也放在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/fntsrlike/AoE2-English-Room-Name","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub – fntsrlike/AoE2-English-Room-Name"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 上了，有興趣的朋友可以前往參考。"}]}]},"title_en":"AoE II: [Mod] English Room Name in Chinese UI","slug":"aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui","aliases":["世紀帝國 II 系列：將中文介面下預設房間名稱改回英文","AoE II: [Mod] English Room Name in Chinese UI"],"created_at":"2018-04-05T17:41:20.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":["aoe","translation"],"moc":["Games"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2018-04-05-aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2018-04-05-aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui.md","_extension":"md"},{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-06-19-principles-behind-the-agile-manifesto","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Fw: 敏捷宣言背後的原則","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本篇可以搭配 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.fntsr.tw/articles/2018/02/21/manifesto-for-agile-software-development/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"敏捷軟體開發宣言"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 閱讀。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下為〈敏捷宣言背後的原則〉（Principles behind the Agile Manifesto）"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":"footnote-label","dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的複本。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h5","props":{"id":"敏捷宣言背後的原則"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"敏捷宣言背後的原則"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我們遵守這些原則："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n我們最優先的任務，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n是透過及早並持續地交付有價值的軟體"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n來滿足客戶需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"竭誠歡迎改變需求，甚至已處開發後期亦然。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n敏捷流程掌控變更，以維護客戶的競爭優勢。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經常交付可用的軟體，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n頻率可以從數週到數個月，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n以較短時間間隔為佳。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"業務人員與開發者"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n必須在專案全程中天天一起工作。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以積極的個人來建構專案，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n給予他們所需的環境與支援，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n並信任他們可以完成工作。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"面對面的溝通"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n是傳遞資訊給開發團隊及團隊成員之間"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n效率最高且效果最佳的方法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可用的軟體是最主要的進度量測方法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"敏捷程序提倡可持續的開發。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n贊助者、開發者及使用者應當能不斷地維持穩定的步調。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持續追求優越的技術與優良的設計，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n以強化敏捷性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"精簡──或最大化未完成工作量之技藝──是不可或缺的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最佳的架構、需求與設計皆來自於"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n能自我組織的團隊。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"團隊定期自省如何更有效率，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n並據之適當地調整與修正自己的行為。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原文如下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h5","props":{"id":"principles-behind-the-agile-manifesto"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Principles behind the Agile Manifesto"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We follow these principles:"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nOur highest priority is to satisfy the customer"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nthrough early and continuous delivery"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nof valuable software."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Welcome changing requirements, even late in"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ndevelopment. Agile processes harness change for"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nthe customer’s competitive advantage."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Deliver working software frequently, from a"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ncouple of weeks to a couple of months, with a"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\npreference to the shorter timescale."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Business people and developers must work"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ntogether daily throughout the project."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Build projects around motivated individuals."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nGive them the environment and support they need,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nand trust them to get the job done."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The most efficient and effective method of"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nconveying information to and within a development"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nteam is face-to-face conversation."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Working software is the primary measure of progress."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agile processes promote sustainable development."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nThe sponsors, developers, and users should be able"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nto maintain a constant pace indefinitely."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Continuous attention to technical excellence"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nand good design enhances agility."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Simplicity–the art of maximizing the amount"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nof work not done–is essential."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The best architectures, requirements, and designs"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nemerge from self-organizing teams."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"At regular intervals, the team reflects on how"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nto become more effective, then tunes and adjusts"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nits behavior accordingly."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kent Beck, Mike Beedle, Arie van Bennekum, Alistair Cockburn, Ward Cunningham ,Martin Fowler, James Grenning, Jim Highsmith, Andrew Hunt, Ron Jeffries, Jon Kern, Brian Marick, Robert C. Martin, Steve Mellor, Ken Schwaber, Jeff Sutherland, Dave Thomas"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"著作權為上述作者所有，2001 年"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n此宣言可以任何形式自由複製，但須附上連同此聲明在內之完整內容。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":true},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Footnotes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Jeff Sutherland, Ken Schwaber, Alistair Cockburn (2001). Manifesto for Agile Software Development. Retrieved from "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://agilemanifesto.org/iso/en/manifesto.htm","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"http://agilemanifesto.org/iso/en/manifesto.htm"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to content","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]}]}]}]},"title_en":"Principles behind the Agile Manifesto","slug":"principles-behind-the-agile-manifesto","aliases":["Fw: 敏捷宣言背後的原則","Principles behind the Agile Manifesto"],"created_at":"2018-06-19T08:12:01.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":[],"moc":["Agile"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2018-06-19-principles-behind-the-agile-manifesto.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2018-06-19-principles-behind-the-agile-manifesto.md","_extension":"md"}]